Kezzia French, 46, thought she had laid her daughter to rest in 1999 .
She was flung at a wall by her father Meyrick Fowler, 24, in Ipswich, Suffolk .
Police failed to tell Ms French she was buried with much of her body parts missing .
Fowler was jailed for four years after throwing her so violently she suffered brain damage and four skull fractures when she died .